* [`F_2`] = [`[$f2]`] [`\textrm{kN}`]

* [`F_3`] = [`[$f3]`] [`\textrm{kN}`]

If [`F_A`] = [`[$fa]`] [`\textrm{kN}`] and [`F_B`] = [`[$fb]`] [`\textrm{kN}`], determine resulrant force and the location of its point of application ([`x`],[`y`]) on the slab from the origin.

[`F_R`] = [_____]{$fr} [`\textrm{kN}`]

[`x`] = [_____]{$x} [`\textrm{m}`]

[`y`] = [_____]{$y} [`\textrm{m}`]


